    <h2 id="why-protein-gummies">Why Protein Gummies Are Trending in 2026</h2>

    <p>The protein supplement market has been dominated by powders, bars, and shakes for decades. Protein gummies represent the newest delivery format — combining the portability of a protein bar with the palatability of candy. For athletes, busy professionals, and anyone struggling to hit their daily protein targets, gummies offer a frictionless way to add 10-20g of protein to any meal or snack without mixing, blending, or chewing through a dense bar.</p>

